'''赫布登布里奇'''（Hebden Bridge）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[西約克郡|西約克郡]]的一個城鎮，位於哈利法克斯以西{{convert|8|mi|km|0}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.calderdale.gov.uk/environment/conservation/conservation-areas/hebden-bridge.pdf |title=Calderdale Council, Conservation areas: Hebden Bridge |access-date=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041534/http://www.calderdale.gov.uk/environment/conservation/conservation-areas/hebden-bridge.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年赫布登布里奇所在卡爾德谷有人口11,549人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.calderdale.gov.uk/council/statistics/ward-information/wardprofiles/calder.pdf |title=Calderdale government information |access-date=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2008-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081016131021/http://www.calderdale.gov.uk/council/statistics/ward-information/wardprofiles/calder.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中赫布登布里奇人口約有4,500人。

